"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-rafael-nadal-french-open-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Rafael Nadal said there is \\\"a big chance\\\" this is his last French Open, but he will need time after the tournament to make that decision.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a big, big chance that going to be my last Roland Garros, but if I have to tell you it's 100% my last Roland Garros, sorry, but I will not, because I cannot predict what's going on,\\\" he said Saturday on the eve of the tournament.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.999999988069476, \"rank\": 6.462245010408454e-09, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.999999988069476, \"rank\": 6.462245010408454e-09, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, a record 14-time French Open champion, plays No.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"4 seed Alexander Zverev in the first round on Monday.\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_Zverev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1224183898900493e-36, \"text\": \"Alexander Zverev\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q